I"A<p>Find your passion that you carry within yourself. Find it as soon as possible and you’ll be great! This is something we can read at almost every corner of the internet.</p>

<p><a href="http://calnewport.com/">Cal Newport</a> in his book <a href="https://amzn.to/2MCcElU">So Good They Can’t Ignore You</a> challenges this view, I think with success. According to <a href="http://calnewport.com/">Newport</a>, (almost) nobody has that inherent, born-with passion. Instead, you have to work hard and you’ll start loving your work. Passion will form with experience.</p>
